    "John Trapp": "The son of Izhar. ] And so first cousin to Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` and Aaron `[char_Aaron_Exo_6]`; for Izhar was brother to Amram their father. { #Ex 6:18 } Sons of Reuben. ] Who, being next neighbours to Korah in the camp, were the sooner corrupted by him. \u201c Uvaque corrupta livorem ducit ab uva. \u2019\u2019\u2014 Juven.\nVer.\n1. The son of Izhar.] And so first cousin to Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` and Aaron `[char_Aaron_Exo_6]`; [v_Exo_6_18] for Izhar was brother to Amram their father. {#Ex 6:18} Sons of Reuben.] Who, being next neighbours to Korah in the camp, were the sooner corrupted by him. \u201c Uvaque corrupta livorem ducit ab uva.\u2019\u2019\u2014Juven.\nVer.",
